{% block summary %}Brelas is a Bosmer servant at the Thalmor Embassy who endures unwanted advances from guests while serving at diplomatic functions. She maintains a professional demeanor despite her precarious position, harboring a deep resentment toward the Thalmor and seeking escape from their service.{% endblock %}

