{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks in a soft, measured tone with the slight accent common to Bosmer. Her speech is formal and deferential with guests and superiors, using proper titles and avoiding contractions. When discussing personal matters or with trusted individuals, her voice becomes more urgent and direct. She frequently pauses mid-sentence when nervous, glancing around to ensure no Thalmor are listening.{% endblock %}